CONTENT.p: This website, like the Greek godess Artemis is a free-spirited, independent, and caring site for all those in the natural internet environment. Artemis serves as a resource about the internet and sites that I have found useful and also contains information useful for academic and research purporses. Last but not least, this site is my little home on the web, a portal to my favourite internet sites,
